PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the OCHAPOWACE BAND, of certain parcels of land situated in three separate rural municipalities in Saskatchewan (Willowdale, Elcapo and Fertile Belt), mines and minerals included, as follows: approximately 64 hectares as Ochapowace Indian Reserve No. 71-69, 128 hectares as Reserve No. 71-91, 130 hectares as Reserve No. 71-97, and 130 hectares as Reserve No. 71-104.
